Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaku Ruifon Sandalkia Diltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pangeran ketiga sekaligus komandan kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi siapa aku sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sahabatnya Cyrus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Salam kenal, Neng Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ternyata orangnya seperti ini...
